{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-f2a44ba1-842b-499b-abe0-e1d9ba5eb41d-18\nfc_073af608-afdb-9c02-abab-95a0e648d7b1_3","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_需求.md","offset":100,"limit":30},"result":{"success":{"content":"2. **`REFERENCED_AGENT_UNKNOWN`**（error）：派生 id 不在角色库。\n3. **`validateParticipantsCharacters`** 对**派生集合**执行。\n4. **`PARTICIPANT_UNKNOWN`**：非空遗留 participants 未知 → **warning**「遗留字段将忽略」；空数组不报错。\n5. **ownerAgentId 不在旧 participants** 但在角色库 → 不得 error。\n\n### 2.2 包内卡生命周期（P0）\n\n| 操作 | 必须行为 |\n|------|----------|\n| 底栏放置新 CallCard | 生成 cardId；追加 `conf.cards[]`；新建 `cards/<cardId>.s-card.json`；画布节点与 conf 一致 |\n| 画布删除 CallCard | 从 `conf.cards[]` 移除；**删除**对应 s-card 文件（若 entryCardId 指向该卡则阻止或强制改入口） |\n| 保存整包 | `editorGraphToBundle` 写回 **conf.cards 与磁盘卡文件并集**（以画布为准），禁止只改 layout 不改 conf |\n| orphan 磁盘卡 | 未在 conf 索引的 s-card → validate `CARD_FILE_ORPHAN` warning；保存时可清理或保留策略写清 |\n\n**禁止：** 仅会话内新增节点，保存后 conf 仍只有打开时的卡列表。\n\n### 2.3 entryCardId 与 effect.critical\n\n| 项 | 口径 |\n|----|------|\n| entryCardId | 包配置或章节浮窗可 Select 本包 cardId；新建包默认指向首张 story 卡或占位 |\n| critical | 读盘保留；投影不丢；Effect 面板 boolean「失败则中止后续」；写回 effect.critical |\n\n### 2.4 ExitCondition 编辑器 v1（P0）\n\n**问题：** 现 `conditionSummary` 仅 UI 人话；写盘用 `base.condition ?? DEFAULT_CONDITION`，改 summary **不改**引擎 condition。\n\n**v1 必须：**\n\n| op | 面板 |","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":294,"fileSize":12906,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_需求.md","readRange":{"startLine":100,"endLine":129},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-f2a44ba1-842b-499b-abe0-e1d9ba5eb41d-18\nfc_073af608-afdb-9c02-abab-95a0e648d7b1_3","startedAtMs":"1784720151845","completedAtMs":"1784720152025"},"model_call_id":"b2981217-1094-4495-bedc-2d366b5462b5-4-ivrq","session_id":"ed19c1d9-bc9f-4ebc-94da-c517ab71378a","timestamp_ms":1784720152013}
