{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-d6e0b317-9465-478c-9ee1-c9aa2294e4ae-20\nfc_744d5ceb-dbde-9760-a430-e1d4bea7e6c4_0","tool_call":{"grepToolCall":{"args":{"pattern":"exitKind|priority|callCardProjection","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/bis/pageBis/storyEditor/package/graph/diskBundleGraph.ts","caseInsensitive":false,"multiline":false,"toolCallId":"call-d6e0b317-9465-478c-9ee1-c9aa2294e4ae-20\nfc_744d5ceb-dbde-9760-a430-e1d4bea7e6c4_0","offset":0},"result":{"success":{"pattern":"exitKind|priority|callCardProjection","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/bis/pageBis/storyEditor/package/graph/diskBundleGraph.ts","outputMode":"content","workspaceResults":{"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine":{"content":{"matches":[{"file":"apps/studioV2/src/bis/pageBis/storyEditor/package/graph/diskBundleGraph.ts","matches":[{"lineNumber":9,"content":"\tcallCardProjectionToDef,","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":10,"content":"} from \"@studio-v2/src/bis/pageBis/storyEditor/package/graph/callCardProjectionMapper\";","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":395,"content":"\t\tcardById.set(proj.cardId, callCardProjectionToDef(proj, original));","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":3,"totalMatchedLines":3,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-d6e0b317-9465-478c-9ee1-c9aa2294e4ae-20\nfc_744d5ceb-dbde-9760-a430-e1d4bea7e6c4_0","startedAtMs":"1784720157106","completedAtMs":"1784720157264"},"model_call_id":"b2981217-1094-4495-bedc-2d366b5462b5-5-zj5a","session_id":"ed19c1d9-bc9f-4ebc-94da-c517ab71378a","timestamp_ms":1784720157254}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-d6e0b317-9465-478c-9ee1-c9aa2294e4ae-22\nfc_744d5ceb-dbde-9760-a430-e1d4bea7e6c4_2","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/03-故事编辑器画布与属性浮窗.md","offset":1,"limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 故事编辑器画布与属性浮窗（代码事实）\n\n> 对照：`apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/**` + `bis/pageBis/storyEditor/**`。  \n> UI 向导需求：[02-新版故事编辑器界面UI设计向导稿](../../AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/02-新版故事编辑器界面UI设计向导稿.md)。  \n> Effect 面板细化：[细化修改7_需求](../../AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改7_需求.md)。  \n> 固化：2026-07-22（V2-T3-8：打开读盘 + 整包保存 + 编辑接线落盘）。\n\n## 1. 壳层结构（认知地图）\n\n```text\nStoryEditorShell\n  ├ StoryEditorTopBar          # chapterTitle 等；保存 → saveStoryPackage_bis\n  ├ StoryEditorCanvasLayer     # React Flow 舞台\n  │    └ StoryCanvasStage / useStoryCanvasGraph\n  ├ FloatingPanelShell         # 属性浮窗（可拖、粘性头尾）\n  │    ├ NodePropertyForm | ChapterPropertyForm\n  │    └ ExitListEditor → ExitEffectsList → ExitEffectPanel\n  ├ BottomToolBar              # placement：CallCard / chapter_end …\n  └ library floats             # 包配置 / 资源挑选等\n```\n\n会话态：节点/边在 `useStoryCanvasGraph` 的 React state；**顶栏保存**经 `editorGraphToBundle` 写回 `data/storis-packages`。\n\n## 2. 节点种类\n\n| React Flow type | data 投影 | 作用 |\n|-----------------|-----------|------|\n| `callCard` | `EditorCallCardProjection` | 通话合同卡 |\n| `chapter` | `EditorChapterNodeData` | `chapter_start` / `chapter_end` |\n| `characterAnchor` | `CharacterAnchorNodeData` | 左侧角色锚点；role handle |\n\n另有轻量 dock 节点（action / commentGroup）：可放置，但属性浮窗策略与 CallCard 分离（见 dock 工厂）。\n\n## 3. 边种类\n\n| edgeKind | 视觉意图 | 真源 |\n|----------|----------|------|\n| `story` | 章节/出口流转（实线） | layout.edges + 会话内连线 |\n| `role` | 卡 → 锚点归属（灰点线） | `ROLE_EDGE_STYLE` |\n| `effect` | attach/unmount（绿虚线等） | `effectEdgeSync.ts` 与 `exit.effects[]` 双向 |\n\n效果边 id：`effect_${sourceNodeId}_${exitId}_${effectId}`，须与 layout 种子边一致以便 reconcile 幂等。\n\n## 4. 选中与属性浮窗（铁律级行为）\n\n- **仅单选**节点打开属性浮窗：`storyCanvasSelection.ts` 中 `params.nodes.length === 1`。  \n- **框选多节点不得开浮窗**（曾出岔子，见 [06](./06-过程岔子与纠正记录.md)）。  \n- `selectionKind`：`callCard` | `chapter`；锚点走角色 FormModal，不是 CallCard 浮窗。  \n- 防御：`toolPolicy?.mode ?? \"\"` 等，避免缺字段炸表单。\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":72,"fileSize":3710,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/03-故事编辑器画布与属性浮窗.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":50},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-d6e0b317-9465-478c-9ee1-c9aa2294e4ae-22\nfc_744d5ceb-dbde-9760-a430-e1d4bea7e6c4_2","startedAtMs":"1784720157112","completedAtMs":"1784720157264"},"model_call_id":"b2981217-1094-4495-bedc-2d366b5462b5-5-zj5a","session_id":"ed19c1d9-bc9f-4ebc-94da-c517ab71378a","timestamp_ms":1784720157263}
